snippet.title: Shaolin Sudoku - gameplay 2
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video of the Windows version of Shaolin Sudoku in 2x speed.
Sharpen your mind by crunching numbers in a relaxing way!
The Yin Yang is a concept of dualism. There must be some darkness in the light and some light in the darkness. Shaolin Sudoku borrows this idea and presents it in an aesthetic Sudoku game.
Shaolin Sudoku is an indie game available for Windows, Linux and Android.
